Patch Set 18:

Generic suggestion- too many levels of inheritance is going to be a maintainance problem in the future as any change that deviates need to be handled differently. Mostly 1 level or 2nd level worst case is good. Inheritance should not be for code reuse(use composition) rather call new code from old code, i.e interface implementation.
